data.name: COZY SWEATFLEECE PERFECT HOODIE
data.shortDescription: Perfect fit. Perfect fabric. Perfect for every day.™
data.c_fit: Fit: Perfect — Not too big, not too small, it’s just right
data.c_similarStylesCopy: Also available in Graphic.
data.c_tabDescription:
A fan favourite with a reputation as the hoodie of all hoodies, this is a pullover sweatshirt with a kanga pocket, dropped shoulders and ribbed trim. It’s made with Aritzia's Cozy Sweatfleece — premium midweight fleece famous for its soft-brushed back, sueded face and cloud-nine plush feel. The best kind of cozy. This garment has been perfected season after season for that just-right fit and feel.

Faded Colours: Our unique wash is achieved through a special technique — instead of dyeing the fabric, we dye the finished garment for a dimensional, sun-faded look and lived-in soft feel.
data.c_tabDetails:
• Content: 78% cotton, 22% polyester, exclusive of ornamentation
  • Care: Machine wash
  • Imported
data.c_tabFeatures:
• Midweight fleece
  • Ribbed cuffs and hem
  • Exclusive Aritzia embroidery
c_tabSizeFit: Length: Hip — Intended to hit at or below the hip
